---
title: Chicken Schnitzel & Roast Capsicum Veggie Toss with Peri-Peri Sauce
description: We’re putting a pep in this chicken schnitzel’s step by drizzling it in a peri peri-honey sauce. It will cut through the
crunch, and sitting it on top of a roast veggie toss will really make this dish fun. You’ll be skipping to the dinner table
in anticipation.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
